replies.body:
Q is just too damn slow! Also really hard to hit your target even if they're right in front of you, if there are minions in the way. I think it's the only support CC that has that issue. If I may, I have a suggestion off the top of my head;

* **(Q) Cosmic Binding** - Automatically calls a Giant Meep to your side for 5 seconds. Your next attack launches the Giant Meep to deal extra damage to the target (based on number of collected Chimes) and slowing. The Giant Meep continues past the target, and stuns if it hits another enemy or a wall.

Basically, Q is an auto-attack buff guaranteed to land on the primary target. Still requires you to time your auto properly to hit the right secondary target or wall.
